{"tid":626124,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖冇乜字] 在雲海中食早餐","createTime":"2018-04-12T01:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T17:12:08.000Z","uid":172556,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bec63902339bbcbeb9c2e7c3f0cecda8e0203880","tid":626124,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qwd342lh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqwd342lh&h=62dcf755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n@Coroico, Bolivia<br />\n<br />\n咁啱本廢青仲喺南美，又見依排多咗南美post，而又有咁多巴絲計劃去南美，所以乘機分享少少自己覺得值得去嘅地方。熱門景點唔講啦，依排幾個post嘅樓豬都介紹得八八九九，所以我就介紹下偏門少少，lihkg比較少人提及嘅地點，等有計劃去南美嘅巴絲可以參考一下。<br />\n<br />\n第一個要介紹嘅就係玻利維亞嘅小村莊Coroico。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zp7j3in0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzp7j3in0&h=75004ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cxe3nfp9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcxe3nfp9&h=b42d2bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vuj6tpze\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvuj6tpze&h=d46183fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/41m9hcur\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F41m9hcur&h=1af78515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/34bh80wg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F34bh80wg&h=27180078&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r4f9kopv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr4f9kopv&h=41dec1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fnyhkr1t\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffnyhkr1t&h=6be0b6e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62764b7e56efaf880c6b29dabcf0ee428fafd478","tid":626124,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislik