","tid":626124,"uid":172556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93507882963e657d93a54fad367362c578fc7bc2","tid":626124,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:42:27.000Z","msg":"玻利維亞details<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"玻利維亞除咗天空之鏡同death road，其實仲有好多野睇，我就喺玻玩咗兩個幾月，巴打有咩可以問，我知嘅話盡答"},{"pid":"4e2a67e7c6da5c3f155173a2228e2314d261bd7e","tid":626124,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e09e356bd4a3f677f806109cf04ab342b9134e10","tid":626124,"uid":172556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93507882963e657d93a54fad367362c578fc7bc2","tid":626124,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:42:27.000Z","msg":"玻利維亞details<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"玻利維亞除咗天空之鏡同death road，其實仲有好多野睇，我就喺玻玩咗兩個幾月，巴打有咩可以問，我知嘅話盡答"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"用咗幾多錢<br />\n住邊<br />\n點去天空之鏡（咩local trip?)<br />\n有咩好食<br />\n溝通點"},{"pid":"af595eb171b7141c934b78187ccc5619d00670b1","tid":626124,"uid":172556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e2a67e7c6da5c3f155173a2228e2314d261bd7e","tid":626124,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e09e356bd4a3f677f806109cf04ab342b9134e10","tid":626124,"uid":172556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93507882963e657d93a54fad367362c578fc7bc2","tid":626124,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:42:27.000Z","msg":"玻利維亞details<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"玻利維亞除咗天空之鏡同death road，其實仲有好多野睇，我就喺玻玩咗兩個幾月，巴打有咩可以問，我知嘅話盡答"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"用咗幾多錢<br />\n住邊<br />\n點去天空之鏡（咩local trip?)<br />\n有咩好食<br />\n溝通點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:02:11.000Z","msg":"洗費： 睇你點玩。(食) 地踎set lunch大約1.5美金，去高檔扒房鋸扒大約10美金; (住) hostel大約5美金一個床位，我自己就多數住bnb式酒店(hostal)，私人房連廁所大約10-15美金。<br />\n<br />\n天空之鏡睇你邊度出發，大部分人係uyuni join tour，有3日tour (帶埋你去睇其他湖啊山啊flamingo reserve，另外有半日嘅日出/日落tour，但我係由另一個city (Tupiza) join 4日tour。<br />\n<br />\n掃街，一定係掃街，我基本上日日都瘋狂掃街。<br />\n<br />\n搵個識conversational英文嘅人應該難過係香港搵個20歲處女。唔識西文嘅話靠身體語言或者google translate"},{"pid":"2dbc307832dae9ab5fe00f5dcdfbc8d9d4696875","tid":626124,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c18d3f19255bb61d9ffd5a3f7b487e3b01c4e50","tid":626124,"uid":172556,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fe520bir\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffe520bir&h=604c360c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n@Caraz, Peru<br />\n<br />\n第二個想介紹嘅係秘魯嘅小村莊Caraz。重點唔係條村本身，而係位於條村附近、被七座雪山圍繞嘅湖Laguna Paron，而七座雪山中，其中一座名為Artesonraju，就係荷里活電影公司Paramount Picture logo入面座雪山。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pceaxdmq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpceaxdmq&h=c4622cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3elbq25r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3elbq25r&h=f1631771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/v4pnhxeb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv4pnhxeb&h=297e83c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3l0pzauh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3l0pzauh&h=48c4799e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https:/